cmd sent need get reply:
init
sent
received, put on queue
ok or error after executed
committed, sync to disk

all msg should end with 'error' or 'committed'


两个节点间消息的传输在一段时间内维持sn的递增，即使一端重新建立连接
    
    connect

    sn = 0
                             sn = 0
                             ack = 1
    sn = 1
    ack =1
    
首先必须有一个可靠的消息传递系统

